Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.35,0:04:56.28,Main01,HASEGAWA,0,0,0,,Just a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.99,0:04:57.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(長谷川)待って！ これは\N芸術的な意味でさ…➡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.28,0:04:59.83,Main01,,0,0,0,,It's art! You see things like this in art textbooks all the time!
